{"title_page": "Municipality of Litija", "text_new": "{{short description|Municipality of Slovenia}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->\n| name                    = Municipality of Litija\n| official_name           =\n| native_name             = ''Ob\u010dina Litija''\n| native_name_lang        = sl<!-- ISO 639-2 code e.g. \"fr\" for French. If more than one, use {{lang}} instead -->\n| settlement_type         = [[Municipalities of Slovenia|Municipality]]\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_alt               =\n| image_caption           = \n| image_shield            =\n| shield_alt              =\n| nickname                =\n| motto                   =\n| image_map               = Karte Litija si.png\n| map_alt                 =\n| map_caption             = Location of the Municipality of Litija in Slovenia\n| pushpin_map             = \n| pushpin_label_position  = \n| pushpin_map_alt         =\n| pushpin_map_caption     = \n| coordinates             = {{coord|46|04|N|14|49|E|region:SI_type:adm1st|display=inline,title}}\n| coor_pinpoint           =\n| coordinates_footnotes   =\n| subdivision_type        = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n| subdivision_name        = {{flag|Slovenia}}\n| established_title       =\n| established_date        =\n| founder                 =\n| seat_type               = <!-- [[Capital (political)|Capital]] -->\n| seat                    =\n| government_footnotes    =\n| leader_party            =\n| leader_title            = Mayor\n| leader_name             = Franci Rokavec\n| unit_pref               = Metric\n| area_footnotes          =\n| total_type              =\n| area_total_km2          = 221\n| area_note               =\n| elevation_footnotes     =\n| elevation_m             = \n| population_footnotes    = <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.stat.si/obcinevstevilkah/Vsebina.aspx?leto=2012&id=81 |title=Litija |work=Ob\u010dine v \u0161tevilkah [Municipalities in Numbers] |accessdate=20 February 2014 |publisher=Statistical Office of the Republic of Slovenia}}</ref>\n| population_total        = 14830\n| population_as_of        = 2010\n| population_density_km2  = 67\n| population_demonym      =\n| population_note         =\n| timezone1               = [[Central European Time|CET]]\n| utc_offset1             = +01\n| timezone1_DST           = [[Central European Summer Time|CEST]]\n| utc_offset1_DST         = +02\n| postal_code_type        =\n| postal_code             =\n| area_code_type          =\n| area_code               =\n| iso_code                =\n| website                 = {{url|http://www.litija.si}}<!-- [http://www.example.com example.com] -->\n| footnotes               = \n}}\nThe '''Municipality of Litija''' ({{IPA-sl|li\u02c8ti\u02d0ja|pron|Sl-Litija.ogg}}; {{lang-sl|Ob\u010dina Litija}}) is a [[Municipalities of Slovenia|municipality]] in central [[Slovenia]]. The seat of the municipality is the town of [[Litija]]. Traditionally the area was part of the [[Upper Carniola|Upper]] and [[Lower Carniola]] regions. The entire municipality is now included in the [[Central Sava Statistical Region]]; until January 2014 it was part of the [[Central Slovenia Statistical Region]]. The population of the municipality is a bit below 15,000.<ref>[http://www.litija.si Litija municipal site]</ref> \n\n==Coat of arms==\nThe municipal coat of arms shows the [[situla (vessel)|situla vase]] from [[Klenik, Litija|Klenik]] (the [[Va\u010de situla]]), the [[Sava|Sava River]], and a boatman pushing his boat, known as a [[punt (boat)|punt]], across the Sava.<ref>[http://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/si-060.html#rib Information on the Coat of Arms]</ref><ref>[http://www.uradni-list.si/1/content?id=48068 The decree about the coat of arms and the flag of the Municipality of Litija]</ref>\n\n==Settlements==\nIn addition to the municipal seat of Litija, the municipality also includes the following settlements:\n{{Div col|colwidth=14em}}\n* [[Berinjek]]\n* [[Bistrica, Litija|Bistrica]]\n* [[Biti\u010de]]\n* [[Boltija]]\n* [[Borovak pri Pol\u0161niku]]\n* [[Breg pri Litiji]]\n* [[Brezje pri Kumpolju]]\n* [[Brezovo, Litija|Brezovo]]\n* [[Brglez, Litija|Brglez]]\n* [[\u010cate\u0161ka Gora]]\n* [[\u010ceplje, Litija|\u010ceplje]]\n* [[Cirku\u0161e, Litija|Cirku\u0161e]]\n* [[Dobje, Litija|Dobje]]\n* [[Dobovica]]\n* [[Dole pri Litiji]]\n* [[Dolgo Brdo, Litija|Dolgo Brdo]]\n* [[Gabrovka, Litija|Gabrovka]]\n* [[Gabrska Gora, Litija|Gabrska Gora]]\n* [[Gobnik]]\n* [[Goli\u0161\u010de]]\n* [[Gorenje Jelenje]]\n* [[Gornje Ravne]]\n* [[Gradi\u0161\u010de, Litija|Gradi\u0161\u010de]]\n* [[Hohovica]]\n* [[Hude Ravne]]\n* [[Javorje pri Gabrovki]]\n* [[Jelenska Reber]]\n* [[Jesenje, Litija|Jesenje]]\n* [[Jevnica]]\n* [[Je\u017eevec]]\n* [[Kal pri Dolah]]\n* [[Kamni Vrh, Litija|Kamni Vrh]]\n* [[Kandr\u0161e, Litija|Kandr\u0161e]]\n* [[Klanec pri Gabrovki]]\n* [[Klenik, Litija|Klenik]]\n* [[Konj, Litija|Konj]]\n* [[Konj\u0161ica]]\n* [[Kresnice]]\n* [[Kresni\u0161ke Poljane]]\n* [[Kresni\u0161ki Vrh]]\n* [[Kr\u017ei\u0161\u010de pri \u010cate\u017eu]]\n* [[Kumpolje]]\n* [[Laze pri Gobniku]]\n* [[Laze pri Va\u010dah]]\n* [[Le\u0161e, Litija|Le\u0161e]]\n* [[Ljube\u017e v Lazih]]\n* [[Lukovec, Litija|Lukovec]]\n* [[Magolnik]]\n* [[Mala Goba]]\n* [[Mala Sela, Litija|Mala Sela]]\n* [[Mamolj]]\n* [[Morav\u010de pri Gabrovki]]\n* [[Morav\u0161ka Gora]]\n* [[Nova Gora, Litija|Nova Gora]]\n* [[Okrog, Litija|Okrog]]\n* [[Pe\u010dice, Litija|Pe\u010dice]]\n* [[Podbukovje pri Va\u010dah]]\n* [[Podpe\u010d pod Skalo]]\n* [[Pod\u0161entjur]]\n* [[Pogonik]]\n* [[Pol\u0161nik]]\n* [[Ponovi\u010de]]\n* [[Potok pri Va\u010dah]]\n* [[Prelesje, Litija|Prelesje]]\n* [[Prevale, Litija|Prevale]]\n* [[Preveg]]\n* [[Pre\u017eenjske Njive]]\n* [[Radgonica]]\n* [[Ravne, Litija|Ravne]]\n* [[Renke]]\n* [[Rib\u010de]]\n* [[R\u017ei\u0161\u010de, Litija|R\u017ei\u0161\u010de]]\n* [[Sava, Litija|Sava]]\n* [[Selce, Litija|Selce]]\n* [[\u0160irmanski Hrib]]\n* [[\u0160iroka Set]]\n* [[Slavina, Litija|Slavina]]\n* [[Slivna]]\n* [[Sopota, Litija|Sopota]]\n* [[Spodnje Jelenje]]\n* [[Spodnji Hoti\u010d]]\n* [[Spodnji Log, Litija|Spodnji Log]]\n* [[Stranski Vrh]]\n* [[Strmec, Litija|Strmec]]\n* [[Suhadole, Litija|Suhadole]]\n* [[\u0160umnik, Litija|\u0160umnik]]\n* [[Teneti\u0161e, Litija|Teneti\u0161e]]\n* [[Tepe, Litija|Tepe]]\n* [[Tihaboj]]\n* [[Tlaka, Litija|Tlaka]]\n* [[Tolsti Vrh, Litija|Tolsti Vrh]]\n* [[Va\u010de]]\n* [[Velika Goba]]\n* [[Velika Preska]]\n* [[Veliki Vrh pri Litiji]]\n* [[Vernek]]\n* [[Vodice pri Gabrovki]]\n* [[Vov\u0161e]]\n* [[Zagorica, Litija|Zagorica]]\n* [[Zagozd, Litija|Zagozd]]\n* [[Zapodje]]\n* [[Zavrh, Litija|Zavrh]]\n* [[Zglavnica]]\n* [[Zgornja Jevnica]]\n* [[Zgornji Hoti\u010d]]\n* [[Zgornji Log]]\n{{Div col end}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commonscat|Municipality of Litija|position=left}}\n* [http://www.litija.si/ Litija municipal site] {{in lang|sl}}\n* [http://geopedia.si/#T105_F408:60_x493073_y100617.73000000001_s12_b4 Municipality of Litija on Geopedia]\n\n{{Litija}}\n{{Municipalities of Slovenia}}\n\n[[Category:Municipality of Litija| ]]\n[[Category:Municipalities of Slovenia|Litija]]\n[[Category:Municipalities in Upper Carniola|Litija]]\n[[Category:Municipalities in Lower Carniola|Litija]]\n[[Category:1994 establishments in Slovenia]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->\n| name                    = Municipality of Litija\n| official_name           =\n| native_name             = ''Ob\u010dina Litija''\n| native_name_lang        = sl<!-- ISO 639-2 code e.g. \"fr\" for French. If more than one, use {{lang}} instead -->\n| settlement_type         = [[Municipalities of Slovenia|Municipality]]\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_alt               =\n| image_caption           = \n| image_shield            =\n| shield_alt              =\n| nickname                =\n| motto                   =\n| image_map               = Karte Litija si.png\n| map_alt                 =\n| map_caption             = Location of the Municipality of Litija in Slovenia\n| pushpin_map             = \n| pushpin_label_position  = \n| pushpin_map_alt         =\n| pushpin_map_caption     = \n| coordinates             = {{coord|46|04|N|14|49|E|region:SI_type:adm1st|display=inline,title}}\n| coor_pinpoint           =\n| coordinates_footnotes   =\n| subdivision_type        = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n| subdivision_name        = {{flag|Slovenia}}\n| established_title       =\n| established_date        =\n| founder                 =\n| seat_type               = <!-- [[Capital (political)|Capital]] -->\n| seat                    =\n| government_footnotes    =\n| leader_party            =\n| leader_title            = Mayor\n| leader_name             = Franci Rokavec\n| unit_pref               = Metric\n| area_footnotes          =\n| total_type              =\n| area_total_km2          = 221\n| area_note               =\n| elevation_footnotes     =\n| elevation_m             = \n| population_footnotes    = <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.stat.si/obcinevstevilkah/Vsebina.aspx?leto=2012&id=81 |title=Litija |work=Ob\u010dine v \u0161tevilkah [Municipalities in Numbers] |accessdate=20 February 2014 |publisher=Statistical Office of the Republic of Slovenia}}</ref>\n| population_total        = 14830\n| population_as_of        = 2010\n| population_density_km2  = 67\n| population_demonym      =\n| population_note         =\n| timezone1               = [[Central European Time|CET]]\n| utc_offset1             = +01\n| timezone1_DST           = [[Central European Summer Time|CEST]]\n| utc_offset1_DST         = +02\n| postal_code_type        =\n| postal_code             =\n| area_code_type          =\n| area_code               =\n| iso_code                =\n| website                 = {{url|http://www.litija.si}}<!-- [http://www.example.com example.com] -->\n| footnotes               = \n}}\nThe '''Municipality of Litija''' ({{IPA-sl|li\u02c8ti\u02d0ja|pron|Sl-Litija.ogg}}; {{lang-sl|Ob\u010dina Litija}}) is a [[Municipalities of Slovenia|municipality]] in central [[Slovenia]]. The seat of the municipality is the town of [[Litija]]. Traditionally the area was part of the [[Upper Carniola|Upper]] and [[Lower Carniola]] regions. The entire municipality is now included in the [[Central Sava Statistical Region]]; until January 2014 it was part of the [[Central Slovenia Statistical Region]]. The population of the municipality is a bit below 15,000.<ref>[http://www.litija.si Litija municipal site]</ref> \n\n==Coat of arms==\nThe municipal coat of arms shows the [[situla (vessel)|situla vase]] from [[Klenik, Litija|Klenik]] (the [[Va\u010de situla]]), the [[Sava|Sava River]], and a boatman pushing his boat, known as a [[punt (boat)|punt]], across the Sava.<ref>[http://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/si-060.html#rib Information on the Coat of Arms]</ref><ref>[http://www.uradni-list.si/1/content?id=48068 The decree about the coat of arms and the flag of the Municipality of Litija]</ref>\n\n==Settlements==\nIn addition to the municipal seat of Litija, the municipality also includes the following settlements:\n{{Div col|colwidth=14em}}\n* [[Berinjek]]\n* [[Bistrica, Litija|Bistrica]]\n* [[Biti\u010de]]\n* [[Boltija]]\n* [[Borovak pri Pol\u0161niku]]\n* [[Breg pri Litiji]]\n* [[Brezje pri Kumpolju]]\n* [[Brezovo, Litija|Brezovo]]\n* [[Brglez, Litija|Brglez]]\n* [[\u010cate\u0161ka Gora]]\n* [[\u010ceplje, Litija|\u010ceplje]]\n* [[Cirku\u0161e, Litija|Cirku\u0161e]]\n* [[Dobje, Litija|Dobje]]\n* [[Dobovica]]\n* [[Dole pri Litiji]]\n* [[Dolgo Brdo, Litija|Dolgo Brdo]]\n* [[Gabrovka, Litija|Gabrovka]]\n* [[Gabrska Gora, Litija|Gabrska Gora]]\n* [[Gobnik]]\n* [[Goli\u0161\u010de]]\n* [[Gorenje Jelenje]]\n* [[Gornje Ravne]]\n* [[Gradi\u0161\u010de, Litija|Gradi\u0161\u010de]]\n* [[Hohovica]]\n* [[Hude Ravne]]\n* [[Javorje pri Gabrovki]]\n* [[Je